org.eclipse.viatra.query.patternlanguage.typing

Interface ITypeSystem

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTypeSystem, EMFTypeSystem, ITypeSystem.NullTypeSystem

    public interface ITypeSystem
    A type system represents the types (classes, or references) provided by a modeling backend.
    No Implement:
    Do not implement directly, rely on AbstractTypeSystem instead.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  ITypeSystem.NullTypeSystem
      An empty implementation of ITypeSystem that can be used by the abstract pattern language module.
